00:44:53.440 --> 00:44:56.880
I write a whole chapter
about him in the book.

00:44:56.880 --> 00:45:02.540
And I was -- I ran into the French
Ambassador who was very senior.

00:45:02.540 --> 00:45:06.520 position:56%
He came from a distinguished family,
Casiasko Morrissey [phonetic].

00:45:06.520 --> 00:45:09.410
His granddaughter's now
